author: Kuokka77
description:
"Glow Bug" (1995) by Basehead/Five Musicians. Borrows heavily from SuperNao's "Sound Traveller" 4ch Amiga mod. To the point that this could be considered a more evolved version in ScreamTracker format despite having a different title.
Amiga art "Stasis (WIP)" by Jok/Dreamweb, 4th at Decrunch 2023 Amiga pixel gfx compo.

ScreamTracker 3.21 and GUS MAX 1.8 hardware mixed.
title: ScreamTracker music: Basehead - Glow Bug (GUS MAX)
